closes #7

skip 'ask mode' for Android 5.1 and later

Asking has been moved from the SIP_CALL_OPTIONS to the account settings
in 5.1. We decided to remove this mode from the button.

Note that the user can still select 'Ask first' in 'Make calls with' and
our button will switch from asking (always use SIP) to not asking (never
use SIP).
Changes by Frank Morgner also apply to Android 5.0 (Tested on Nexus 5)
